进一步分解，实现无限分解深度","Qwen-Image-Layered 是一个能够将图像分解为多个 RGBA 图层的模型，通过图层分解实现固有的可编辑性。\n\nQwen-Image-Layered 是阿里巴巴通义千问团队开发的模型，能够将图像分解为多个 RGBA 图层。这种分层表示解锁了固有的可编辑性：每个图层都可以独立操作而不影响其他内容。\n主要特性：\n固有可编辑性：每个图层都可以独立操作而不影响其他内容\n高保真基础操作：支持调整大小、重新定位和重新着色，语义组件物理隔离\n可变图层分解：不限于固定数量的图层 - 可根据需要分解为 3、4、8 或更多图层\n递归分解：任何图层都可以进一步分解，实现无限分解深度"],"color":"#1B252B","bgcolor":"#141B1F","boxcolor":"#3E4D54"},{"id":171,"type":"KSampler","pos":[1912,514],"size":[225,589],"flags":{"collapsed":false},"order":16,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"模型","name":"model","type":"MODEL","link":259},{"localized_name":"正面条件","name":"positive","type":"CONDITIONING","link":285},{"localized_name":"负面条件","name":"negative","type":"CONDITIONING","link":286},{"localized_name":"Latent图像","name":"latent_image","type":"LATENT","link":276},{"localized_name":"种子","name":"seed","type":"INT","widget":{"name":"seed"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"步数","name":"steps","type":"INT","widget":{"name":"steps"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"cfg","name":"cfg","type":"FLOAT","widget":{"name":"cfg"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"采样器名称","name":"sampler_name","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"sampler_name"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"调度器","name":"scheduler","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"scheduler"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"降噪","name":"denoise","type":"FLOAT","widget":{"name":"denoise"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"Latent","name":"LATENT","type":"LATENT","slot_index":0,"links":[260]}],"properties":{"Node name for S&R":"KSampler","enableTabs":false,"tabWidth":65,"tabXOffset":10,"hasSecondTab":false,"secondTabText":"Send Back","secondTabOffset":80,"secondTabWidth":65,"cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.5.1","ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"version":"7.7","input_ue_unconnectable":{}}},"widgets_values":[179871246980871,"randomize",20,2.5,"euler","simple",1]},{"id":172,"type":"ModelSamplingAuraFlow","pos":[1537,734],"size":[225,104],"flags":{"collapsed":false},"order":2,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_nam